'''''GigaScience''''' 于2012年创刊，是一本[[同行评议|同行评议]]的[[科学期刊|科学期刊]]<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Goodman L, Edmunds SC, Basford AT | title = Large and linked in scientific publishing | journal = GigaScience | volume = 1 | issue = 1 | pages = 1 | date = July 2012 | pmid = 23587310 | pmc = 3617448 | doi = 10.1186/2047-217X-1-1 | url = https://academic.oup.com/gigascience/article/1/1/2047-217X-1-1/2656138 | access-date = 2020-09-02 | archive-date = 2020-08-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200813071658/https://academic.oup.com/gigascience/article/1/1/2047-217X-1-1/2656138 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。该刊发表[[生物医学|生物医学]]和[[生命科学|生命科学]]领域的[[大数据|大数据]]研究和大数据集<ref>{{Cite web |last=Davies |first=Kevin |name-list-format=vanc |url=http://www.bio-itworld.com/2011/09/23/big-data-bgi-gigascience.html |title=Big Data, BGI and GigaScience |publisher=Bio-IT World |date=2011-09-23 |access-date=2016-07-11 |archive-date=2020-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201025043036/http://www.bio-itworld.com/2011/09/23/big-data-bgi-gigascience.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，主编为Scott Edmunds。''GigaScience'' 归[[华大基因|华大基因]]（BGI）旗下的GigaScience出版社所有。该刊最初由[[BioMed_Central|BioMed Central]]（隶属于[[施普林格·自然|施普林格·自然]]）和[[华大基因|华大基因]]（BGI）联合出版<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.duraspace.org/bgi-and-biomed-central-launch-gigascience-big-data-journal |title=BGI and BioMed Central Launch GigaScience "Big Data" Journal |date=2012-07-23 |publisher=DuraSpace |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130310092116/http://www.duraspace.org/bgi-and-biomed-central-launch-gigascience-big-data-journal |archive-date=2013-03-10 |access-date=2016-07-27 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。自2016年起，GigaScience出版社转为与[[牛津大学出版社|牛津大学出版社]]（Oxford University Press，简称OUP）合作，致力于推动数据共享、公开透明的[[同行评议|同行评议]]和作者署名等方面的最佳实践<ref>{{Cite web |last=Oxford University Press |url=https://www.eurekalert.org/pub_releases/2016-10/oupu-gjt102716.php |title=GigaScience joins the Oxford University Press journals program |publisher=EurekAlert! |date=2016-10-27 |access-date=2017-06-22 |archive-date=2020-10-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201018145544/https://www.eurekalert.org/pub_releases/2016-10/oupu-gjt102716.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2018年，''GigaScience''荣获{{Translink|en|Association of American Publishers|美國出版商協會|美國出版商協會}}颁发的综合类期刊出版创新奖—{{Translink|en|PROSE Awards|专业与学术杰出出版奖|专业与学术杰出出版奖}}（PROSE奖）<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://proseawards.com/winners/2018-award-winners/|title=2018 Award Winners|website=PROSE Awards|access-date=2019-06-14|archive-date=2020-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125125602/https://proseawards.com/winners/2018-award-winners/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==GigaDB==
为了有效存储期刊发表的大数据集，''GigaScience''与[[中国国家基因库|中国国家基因库]]（China National GeneBank，简称CNGB）合作创建了期刊自有数据库[[GigaDB|GigaDB]]<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Xiao SZ, Armit C, Edmunds S, Goodman L, Li P, Tuli MA, Hunter CI | title = Increased interactivity and improvements to the GigaScience database, GigaDB | journal = Database | volume = 2019 | date = January 2019 | pmid = 30753480 | pmc = 6376146 | doi = 10.1093/database/baz016 }}</ref>。

==文摘和索引==
''GigaScience''被Index Medicus/MEDLINE/PubMed<ref name=MEDLINE>{{cite web |url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/nlmcatalog/101596872 |title=GigaScience |work=NLM Catalog |publisher=[[National_Center_for_Biotechnology_Information|National Center for Biotechnology Information]] |access-date=2018-06-02 |archive-date=2020-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200605024619/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/nlmcatalog/101596872 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、[[科学引文索引|科学引文索引]]（Science Citation Index，缩写：SCI）<ref name=ISI>{{cite web |url=http://mjl.clarivate.com/ |title=Master Journal List |publisher=[[Clarivate_Analytics|Clarivate Analytics]] |work=Intellectual Property & Science |access-date=2018-06-02 |archive-date=2020-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200620100246/https://mjl.clarivate.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>和[[Scopus|Scopus]]收录。根据[[期刊引证报告|期刊引证报告]]（Journal Citation Reports，JCR），该刊2019年[[影响因子|影响因子]]为5.999<ref name="WoS">{{cite book |title=2019 Journal Citation Reports|title-link=Journal Citation Reports|publisher=[[Clarivate_Analytics|Clarivate Analytics]]|year=2020|isbn=|edition=Science|series=[[Web_of_Science|Web of Science]]|location=|pages=|chapter=GigaScience}}</ref>。

